# /etc/praxis/web.env — environment for the praxis-web container.
#
# Copy to /etc/praxis/web.env on the VPS and fill in real values. This
# file is intentionally empty today; the landing page needs no runtime
# config. Auth env vars arrive in STORY-04.
#
# Wire the file into the systemd unit by adding to praxis-web.service:
#   ExecStart=... --env-file /etc/praxis/web.env ...
# and uncommenting the corresponding line if/when env is added.
